data.title: David B Robbins
data.meta_description: David B Robbins was appointed Executive Director/Chief Operating Officer of the Federal Trade Commission by Chairwoman Edith Ramirez on Sept. 9, 2013. He leads the agency's administrative operations, including human resources/human capital management, financial operations, information technology, administrative services, and records and filings.
data.text:
Has "David B Robbins" contacted you?

Important: David B Robbins will never demand money, make threats, tell you to transfer money, or promise you a prize. FTC employees will not ask you for personal or financial information, or call to notify you that you’ve been a victim of identity theft. If someone says they’re from the FTC and demands money, they’re a scammer. Don’t pay them or give them any personal information.

Learn more about How to Avoid Government Impersonation Scams

If you have been targeted by an illegal business practice or scam, contact your local law enforcement authorities, and report it to the FTC.
